during the war.

142
00:11:28,453 --> 00:11:31,752
Said that when it came to killing
vampires, you were the best.

143
00:11:33,126 --> 00:11:34,821
I'm going after her.

144
00:11:35,094 --> 00:11:36,959
I'm gonna get her back.

145
00:11:38,599 --> 00:11:41,969
I just thought I should let you know
in case you wanted to come along.

146
00:11:43,105 --> 00:11:45,801
Figure I could use someone
like you by my side.

147
00:11:51,983 --> 00:11:53,143
Okay.

148
00:12:12,974 --> 00:12:16,842
Thank you for meeting with me on
such short notice, Monsignors.

149
00:12:17,379 --> 00:12:21,042
Monsignor Chamberlain has
informed us of the situation.

150
00:12:21,584 --> 00:12:23,415
Your family is in our prayers.

151
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:24,569
PRIEST: Thank you.

152
00:12:25,021 --> 00:12:28,149
I come before you because I
need my authority reinstated.

153
00:12:29,493 --> 00:12:30,551
On what grounds?

154
00:12:33,698 --> 00:12:35,563
This was a vampire attack.

155
00:12:36,101 --> 00:12:37,432
Vampires?

156
00:12:39,338 --> 00:12:40,388
(CHUCKLING)

157
00:12:40,607 --> 00:12:44,407
Nonsense. We've had no reports of
any escapes from the reservations.

158
00:12:44,778 --> 00:12:48,009
