of Wasteland bandits.

159
00:12:48,182 --> 00:12:49,877
Monsignor, the boy was clear.

160
00:12:50,018 --> 00:12:52,452
The boy was mistaken.

161
00:12:53,087 --> 00:12:54,782
There is no vampire menace.

162
00:12:55,190 --> 00:12:58,887
The Wastelands are a haven for
the lawless and the immoral.

163
00:12:58,961 --> 00:13:02,871
To send a Priest out there after such a
lot would be both ridiculous and futile.

164
00:13:03,133 --> 00:13:06,694
This is best left
to the local authority.

165
00:13:08,439 --> 00:13:12,899
Monsignor Orelas, this man has been
of great service to the Church.

166
00:13:13,712 --> 00:13:16,902
If it weren't for the Priests, we
would have been overrun by the...

167
00:13:16,916 --> 00:13:20,317
We are well aware of his accomplishments,
Monsignor Chamberlain.

168
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:22,581
Thank you. You may sit.

169
00:13:24,825 --> 00:13:26,452
I am begging you.

170
00:13:28,163 --> 00:13:29,460
Allow me to find her.

171
00:13:30,098 --> 00:13:32,726
You must understand
something, Priest.

172
00:13:33,402 --> 00:13:37,133
The sanctity of these
walls is absolute.

173
00:13:37,607 --> 00:13:40,317
And the citizens from the
Cities have complete faith

174
00:13:40,445 --> 00:13:42,913
in the Church's ability
to keep them safe.

175
00:13:43,181 --> 00:13:45,274
You will not shake that faith.

176
00:13:45,784 --> 00:13:48,184
What good is that faith
when it's a lie?

177
00:13:48,286 --> 00:13:52,620
Questioning the authority of the
Clergy is absolutely forbidden.

178
00:13:52,826 --> 00:13:54,996
If you take any action
to leave the Cities,

179
00:13:54,998 --> 00:13:57,662
it will be seen as an act of
aggression against the Church.

180
00:13:57,665 --> 00:14:01,133
You will be stripped from the Order
and excommunicated immediately.

181
00:14:01,136 --> 00:14:02,276
Do I make myself clear?

182
00:14:04,540 --> 00:14:08,271
I said do I make
myself clear, Father?

183
00:14:09,947 --> 00:14:11,539
Yes, Monsignor.

184
00:14:15,018 --> 00:14:16,610
Try to remember your vow,

185
00:14:17,354 --> 00:14:21,347
to go against the Church
is to go against God.

186
