a good idea, mister.

236
00:19:52,385 --> 00:19:53,435
Well, I'll be damned.

237
00:19:58,926 --> 00:20:02,555
Vampires are a vicious lot.

238
00:20:02,964 --> 00:20:05,398
I have seen a vampire

239
00:20:05,802 --> 00:20:08,771
