247
00:20:31,331 --> 00:20:32,389
Show's over.

248
00:20:32,733 --> 00:20:34,394
And it's time for you to go.

249
00:20:34,469 --> 00:20:36,801
Give me one good reason
why I should.

250
00:20:39,942 --> 00:20:41,307
